<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idd262d653-4ef6-11f1-9110-db228fde61c5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1992—<ref href="/us/pl/102/538">Pub. L. 102–538</ref> substituted “waived” for “signed a waiver of”.</p>
